title: Stardock Start8 1.20 + Patch (T3D1)
description:
Stardock Start8 1.20 + Patch (T3D1)


        Microsoft Windows 8 is shipped without the "Start" menu.
              Stardock heard the cries from Windows 8 users.
               We put the "Start" menu back in Windows 8.
           We accurately recreated the most used desktop feature
            billions of users depend on every day and packed it 
                       with additional functionality.         



              1] Install App & Exit
              2] Copy Patch To Install Directory
              4] Open It & Click Patch
              3] Done, Enjoy
